AHHH I FORGOT ABOUT THIS!

heeeeeey guyssssss!!
16 photos of ya girl BIMMYYYY coming at you from this beautiful GARDEN OF GODDESSES. There's lots of leg, thighs, some side butt, and even MORE of this set coming very soon with a certain friend.

... and yes. that friend is of course @arryn! She has her solos up on her page as well, then we'll be releasing the photos we did together!!


BUT NOT ONLY THAT! We shot a BUNCH of different sets together, and this is the first of many, so stay tuned to both our pages for the goods. 🤤 🤤 🤤

posts.subject: Loose Silk Shirt
posts.body:
Got some more photos back from a shoot with Wes today!

This set is really peaceful to me. A long walk in the woods, loose silk shirt, and forgot my shorts on a tree somewhere 😂

Definitely one of the more revealing sets I’ve done, but it feels very free and natural in this setting. Just being one with nature and enjoying the afternoon sun…

🌤🌳🦌🍃👖

posts.subject: Banana Deepthroat
posts.body: Gag reflex?? 😳🍌🍌 I CAN’T BELIEVE I DID THIS FULLY TOPLESS! How far down do you think I can go as I deep throat? Might take a few tries to get it right…

posts.subject: Harley Quinn
posts.body:
It's Harley Quinn time!!! (2/2)

This is by far the most revealing set I've done - but how can you not get a little crazy with it when you're portraying Harley? It just fits the character so well. I really hope you all enjoy!!!

This is set 2 of 2! Based off the results from my poll, each set has a mixture of every pose / look. You'll be able to tell that I am absolutely feelin' myself in this outfit.
